sci_fi_thriller.title: Sci-Fi Thriller
sci_fi_thriller.description: Extraterrestrial lifeforms, alien worlds, time travel and more. These movies always have another puzzle to unlock.

284009.title: Turbulent Skies
284009.description: A pilot-less plane malfunctions midflight, and the military threatens to destroy it before it crashes—but the one man who can fix it is on the ground.

286059.title: Lost Time
286059.description: Two sisters stop on the side of the road and are blinded by a mysterious light. When the light fades, one is missing. Could it be aliens?

287458.title: Ghidorah, the Three-Headed Monster
287458.description: After a meteorite unleashes a three-headed beast upon Tokyo, Mothra tries to unite with Godzilla and Rodan to battle the extraterrestrial threat.

289797.title: The Divide
289797.description: Survivors of a nuclear attack endure days in a basement, only to be driven mad by dwindling supplies and fear of what lies outside their bunker.

300161.title: Cube 2: Hypercube
300161.description: Finding themselves trapped in cube-shaped rooms where the laws of physics are suspended, eight strangers must unlock the cubes' secrets to stay alive.

300162.title: Cube Zero
300162.description: When a group of eight strangers awaken in a trap-filled maze, one young man endeavors to save an innocent woman trapped inside.

300846.title: The Wraith
300846.description: A mysterious black turbo racing car appears and challenges a murderous gang leader to a series of races. The driver's identity may surprise everyone.

302262.title: Unforgettable
302262.description: When a forensic scientist is accused of murdering his wife, he tests a memory-leeching drug that will help him find her killer and clear his name.

306917.title: The Arrival
306917.description: An astronomer discovers intelligent alien life, but the aliens are keeping a deadly secret and will do anything to keep him from learning the truth.

314137.title: APP
314137.description: After a night of partying in the dorms, Anna wakes up to find that a new app on her phone. Initially helpful and clever, IRIS soon begins behaving in cruel, mysterious ways.

316459.title: Cube
316459.description: Seven strangers find themselves imprisoned in a seemingly endless maze filled with deadly traps and must fight to escape,  despite the odds.

321859.title: Enter Nowhere
321859.description: In this bizarre thriller, different timelines intersect when three strangers unexpectedly arrive at a cabin in the woods and are unable to leave.

326249.title: Incident at Raven's Gate
326249.description: Ex-con Eddie Cleary gets a job working on his older brother's isolated farm. It's not long before bizarre things start happening, dead birds falling out of the sky, family pets attacking their owners, strange apparitions beginning to appear, and people who had been normal suddenly going insane.

326989.title: Weaponized
326989.description: A detective doubts the guilt of a veteran accused of a mass shooting and uncovers a dangerous military operation with unimaginable consequences.

332939.title: Right at your Door
332939.description: With Los Angeles under sieges by toxic bombs, Brad and Lexi struggle to survive with little supply, limited time and no information.

341531.title: Nightmare Code
341531.description: Nightmare Code is an independent sci-fi thriller about behavior recognition technology, behavior modification, 24/7 surveillance and artificial intelligence.

343302.title: Star Leaf
343302.description: Three friends fight to stay alive after finding extra-terrestrial marijuana deep in the woods and accidentally provoking the alien forces guarding it.

357489.title: CO2
357489.description: A mysterious deadly vapor suffocates a small American coal town. Based on actual events.

364445.title: Area Q
364445.description: An investigative journalist whose world is turned upside-down when his son disappears is sent to Brazil to investigate close encounter sightings.

367626.title: 2012: Doomsday
367626.description: As the date of the apocalypse nears, several strangers travel to a temple in Mexico to prevent an ancient prophecy from destroying the world.

367633.title: 500 MPH Storm
367633.description: In this tale of man vs. nature, one man must save his family after an experiment gone wrong unleashes deadly hurricanes capable of destroying America.

377052.title: Counter Clockwise
377052.description: A scientist accidentally invents a time machine, zapping himself six months into the future where he is wanted for murder in this dark, sci-fi comedy.

382220.title: Campus Code
382220.description: A sense of something being amiss on their college campus, sends a group of students on a quest to find answers and survive unknown forces. Battling Guards, Griefers and at times each other, they'll have to fight to make it out alive from this other-worldly campus.

382248.title: Asteroid: Final Impact
382248.description: Nobody believes a disgraced whistleblower scientist who detects a giant asteroid barreling toward Earth leaving him alone to save the planet.

387301.title: Conspiracy Theory
387301.description: A group of conspiracy theorists in Nevada learn the unsettling reason as to why the government has covered up the existence of alien life.

392046.title: Darkening Sky
392046.description: When a student discovers extraterrestrials exist and are taking possession of humans, he soon suspects that he is the center of the aliens' plan.

396740.title: The Frame
396740.description: Two strangers find their lives collide in an impossible way. Taking on the very root of fate, destiny, and their own existence, Alex and Sam race through an ever-changing universe while being pursued by a demonic man determined to erase the world.

403283.title: Outpost 11
403283.description: In a steam-powered world, the lives of three soldiers manning a listening post in the Arctic are plunged into chaos when the warning light blinks off.

403311.title: B4
403311.description: Three friends find themselves trapped in an underground parking garage with doorways leading into the past and future and floors that repeat themselves for eternity. They must struggle to keep their sanity, if not their lives.

456859.title: Control
456859.description: A morally deviant inmate on death row agrees to be a test subject for a new behavior modification drug in order to get a second chance at life.

456943.title: Altered Hours
456943.description: An exhausted young man gets a grim look into his own future when he experiments with a new drug and experiences a vision of himself as a wanted man.

457150.title: The Cure
457150.description: A medical researcher discovers that cancer is too profitable to be cured. Caught in a vast and sinister conspiracy, she begins the fight for her life.

460884.title: After the Dark
460884.description: Students are forced to confront their own fears and biases when their professor sets up a class exercise that is sure to change all their lives.

460948.title: Atlas Shrugged (Pt. 1)
460948.description: A brave, resourceful businesswoman begins to question everything she knows when evidence of a government conspiracy begins to take shape.

461393.title: The Black Dawn
461393.description: Thirteen college students inexplicably survive a deadly plague and puzzle out what has killed the people of Los Angeles and turned the sky black.

463151.title: Implanted
463151.description: When Ethan (Justice Leak) begins to experience flashes of disjointed and bewildering memories he desperately attempts to put together the pieces of his life, but is he prepared for the truth?

464516.title: Jack's Apocalypse
464516.description: An addict ex-politician whose life has spiraled out of control finds redemption when challenged with keeping his sister-in-law and niece alive during the apocalypse.

465158.title: The Medusa Touch
465158.description: A French detective in London tries to unravel the mystery of a hospital patient with telekinetic powers, whose anxieties manifest in actual disasters.

465163.title: The Boys From Brazil
465163.description: A Nazi-hunter chases infamous Dr. Josef Mengele, who has escaped to Paraguay to revive the Third Reich

465922.title: Mysterious
465922.description: On an island in the Bermuda triangle,a film producer cannot resist the siren call when he sees a dolphin push a beautiful, unconscious woman ashore.

466391.title: 7 Splinters in Time
466391.description: A detective arrives at a crime scene to identify a body, which, shockingly, is his own, and discovers he might also be his own prime suspect.

466613.title: The Scopia Effect
466613.description: A depressed woman undergoes hypnotherapy, releasing dark forces from across time as she experiences past lives that should have stayed forgotten.

466657.title: Rumor From Ground Control
466657.description: A courageous journalist chases after the truth surrounding the mysterious deaths of a crew of astronauts in this conspiracy thriller.

468579.title: Fugitive Mind
468579.description: A tech engineer suffering from memory loss makes the shocking discovery that the company he works for has programmed him to commit violent crimes.

468930.title: The Precipice
468930.description: In a post-apocalyptic world, an ex-soldier and her prisoner traverse enemy territory to locate a place that holds the key to their nation’s salvation.

468958.title: A Dark Matter
468958.description: A young artist slips into a surreal realm where he sets out to uncover the disturbing truth about the mysterious disappearance of his girlfriend.

474269.title: Cold Zone
474269.description: A man interrupts his family vacation in Alaska to team up with a retired environmental expert and save the world from a flash-freezing storm.

475054.title: Painkillers
475054.description: A squad of US Marines awakens in a hospital with no memories of their mission in Afghanistan, nor the otherworldly artifact they were sent to find.

475833.title: Solar Destruction
475833.description: When a math prodigy discovers a new way of predicting solar flares, he tries to warn of an impending catastrophe, but no one in power will listen.

475850.title: Dark Skies
475850.description: A scientist discovers that a disaster relief company is creating environmental havoc, and attempts to neutralize the crisis before it's too late.

475852.title: Storm Chasers
475852.description: After a twister takes her husband’s life, a storm chaser throws herself into her work and discovers a lab where experiments are causing tornadoes.

475991.title: Nuclear Hurricane
475991.description: With a massive natural disaster coming and a nuclear meltdown just around the corner, a band of scientists and rescuers fight to save an entire city.

476704.title: Containment
476704.description: When neighbors in an apartment complex wake up to see they've been sealed inside by strangers in hazmat suits, they start to turn on each other.

478727.title: Pandemic
478727.description: A virus tears through New Mexico. A local veterinarian teams up with an eccentric rancher to expose the true threat and save mankind.

480242.title: The Kovak Box
480242.description: David Norton is used to being in control. As a best-selling author, he decides the fate of his characters; his heroes, his villains, their lives and deaths. But what happens when his fictional world becomes all too real? When David arrives in an idyllic Mediterranean island for a conference, his fiancee receives a strange call and jumps to her death from their hotel balcony. As he begins piecing answers together, people start inexplicably committing suicide all around him. Now David has become the reluctant hero of his own living story, and this time he has no idea how it will end.

486378.title: Disconnect
486378.description: A mysterious phone that connects a college student with her murdered mother in the past helps her prevent it and save her own life in the process.

486569.title: Miracle Mile
486569.description: Good natured musician learns that the U.S. has fired a nuclear warhead which means that the end of the world is about an hour away.

486868.title: Miami Magma
486868.description: Follows prodigy vulcanologist Antoinette Vitrini and her sister Emily as they attempt to blow the whistle on an illegal oil drilling scheme before it sets off the eruption of a super-volcano directly beneath Miami.

487951.title: Earthstorm
487951.description: A massive asteroid's impact on the moon shifts its orbit, causing massive storms on earth due to the sudden changes in ocean tides.

489450.title: Weather Wars
489450.description: Washington haunting series of weather disasters, devastating the city. Two brothers - sons of a recognized scientist and meteorologist - begin an investigation to explain the unexpected attacks of nature.

489702.title: Dark Descent
489702.description: When investigating the mysterious death of a group of underwater miners, a man discovers a dangerous conspiracy that could turn on him next.

490007.title: Involution
490007.description: After a series of events sends the earth into a terrible, inhuman mechanism that turns back Darwin’s Theory of Evolution, nothing is certain.

490254.title: Hayflick Limit
490254.description: After a woman wakes up in a lab alone, she must escape and figure out the reason why she was selected for a bizarre age experiment.

493214.title: Flashburn
493214.description: A man who is the only one who knows the cure for a global and deadly virus finds himself sealed off in a warehouse after a car crash with no memory.

495438.title: Landing Lake
495438.description: A team of technicians sent to repair a satellite station become spellbound by an unseen entity in nearby lake to give into their most primal desires.

495464.title: Prodigy
495464.description: A self-medicating widower’s broken spiral changes when his son asks him to go on a trek to a secret location for a divine message to save humanity.

496064.title: Motel Mist
496064.description: At an unusual motel on the outskirts of Bangkok, four lives intertwine in a series of tales featuring the depraved, the hopeful, and the supernatural.

499235.title: CTRL
499235.description: After a lonely computer programmer creates an AI device that can evolve and adapt, it overtakes his life and threatens to destroy his loved ones.

499281.title: Lunopolis
499281.description: Two documentary filmmakers discover news about the moon, which leads them down a dangerous path with a potentially real conspiracy theory.

499390.title: Paradox
499390.description: A team of scientists develop a way to travel through time, but after a colleague visits the future, they learn the project could kill them all.

501439.title: Patient 001
501439.description: A woman allows a doctor to clone her dying husband with his DNA. The baby she delivers revives her husband, but he and the baby can never coexist.

502452.title: Eyes Behind the Stars
502452.description: The sense of being stalked makes a photographer and his model halt a forest photo shoot, but the film later shows what appears to be aliens lurking.

504461.title: Crystal's Shadow
504461.description: Stalked by a strange man and haunted by memories of an abusive mother, a young woman is about to learn the truth about her otherworldly nature.

505469.title: Black Hollow Cage
505469.description: Living in a secluded forest home with her father, a young girl discovers a strange black cube that seemingly delivers messages from her future self.

506679.title: New Rose Hotel
506679.description: In the future, two businessmen, who are hired to steal secrets from a rival, enlist the aid of a beautiful and mysterious, but volatile, call girl.

506700.title: Atomic Twister
506700.description: When tornadoes hit a nuclear power plant, catastrophe is unleashed on a small town. Can anyone stop this path of destruction before it’s too late?

507433.title: The Stepford Wives
507433.description: A modern woman and her family, new to the town of Stepford, starts to see that the wives in town are suspiciously perfect and submissive to their men.

510906.title: The Amaranth
510906.description: When a debilitating stroke leads a man to move into an elite but cult-like retirement community, his younger wife soon discovers its sinister secrets.

511840.title: Jackrabbit
511840.description: When a friend's suicide leaves behind a mysterious computer drive, a hacker and a computer technician attempt to decipher the message left in his wake.

514216.title: Time Lapse
514216.description: Three friends scheming to misuse a mysterious machine that takes photos 24 hours into the future begin to see disturbing and scary pictures develop.

517545.title: The Field
517545.description: A hail mary effort to save their marriage leads an amateur photographer and his wife to buy a farmhouse they discover is locked inside a secret world.

518162.title: By Dawn
518162.description: A former Marine suffering from severe PTSD prepares his family for war as the deadline for an alien invasion approaches in this sci-fi thriller.

519046.title: Robin Cook's Acceptable Risk
519046.description: A scientific drug that could be a miraculous breakthrough comes with a side effect both terrifying and potentially linked to the Salem Witch Trials.

519468.title: Skyquake
519468.description: After strange sounds coming from the sky go viral on social media, a reclusive man is convinced that the culprit of the sounds is now in his home.

530233.title: The 11th Patient
530233.description: A doctor who specializes in treating trauma patients tries to use virtual reality technology in order to rescue a comatose child and catch a criminal.

531788.title: Beyond the Sky
531788.description: A man who attends UFO conventions to disprove alien abductions meets a woman who is days away from age 28 and claims to be abducted every 7 years.

532480.title: The Mourning
532480.description: When a soldier reappears after being gone for twenty years, his loved ones try to solve the mystery of what happened to him, and why he hasn’t aged.

540054.title: Rupture
540054.description: A single mom tries to break free from a mysterious organization that seeks to expose her to her deepest fear in order to reveal her true self.

540908.title: The Cyclotron
540908.description: In 1944, memories of love and nuclear physics oppose forces, as an Allied spy sets out to execute a Berlin scientist who knows how to build an A-bomb.

543756.title: Hostile
543756.description: A woman who is a survivor in an apocalyptic era, fights to survive against hunger, injury and disturbing creatures that only come out at nighttime.

549709.title: Paper Man
549709.description: A college prank leads to murder when four students create a fictitious person to get a credit card, using the school’s computer to erase the evidence.

550641.title: Fire From Below
550641.description: The hunt for an alternative energy source unleashes a toxic lithium that reaches the earth's surface, setting off a devastating series of events.

550814.title: Yo Soy Otro (Others)
550814.description: A punto de darse un plomazo, José descubre con horror un virus que carcome su propia piel y escarmienta en pellejo ajeno pues todos son él mismo.

554427.title: Radio Silence
554427.description: An elite Special Forces unit accepts a mission to retrieve a spy satellite from the desert, only to become stranded, facing a mysterious enemy.

555044.title: Battle of Memories
555044.description: A cutting-edge procedure that can switch a person’s mind with another and clear memories goes wrong for a man who gets the mind of a serial killer.

555378.title: Perfect
555378.description: A disturbed young man seeks treatment in a clinic. Given an unusual therapy, he seems to respond well, until things take a dark turn.

555701.title: Timebomb
555701.description: A man consults a psychiatrist for help after he begins suffering an unrelenting series of terrifying flashbacks.

557842.title: The Unseen
557842.description: A deadbeat dad returns years later to bond with his troubled daughter. When she goes missing, he must risk it all to find her as he turns invisible.

559203.title: Sinkhole
559203.description: After a massive sinkhole swallows an entire town, a group of teenagers must fight for their lives when their bus becomes trapped underground.

559740.title: One Step Ahead
559740.description: A private investigator, hired to find the killer of a widow’s husband after 25 years as a cold case, discovers a mystery more shocking than death.

562530.title: Interpreters
562530.description: When the residents of a small community are slowly picked off, the killer’s unusual calling card brings in a former black-ops soldier to investigate.

562824.title: Threshold
562824.description: During an apocalyptic event, a couple risks redemption at the hands of an otherworldly intruder who knows details about their tragic past.

564305.title: Fissure
564305.description: A routine call for a detective at a noted scientist's home turns into a deadly and mind-bending mystery that offers a chance to change his own fate.

566112.title: Dark Encounter
566112.description: A family, grieving from the loss of an 8-year-old child, encounters an eerie, unsettling phenomenon that seems bent on terrorizing them—but also may hold the key to the truth behind the girl’s tragic disappearance.

569076.title: The Honeymoon Phase
569076.description: For a $50,000 bounty, a young couple becomes guinea pigs in a month-long futuristic experiment that sequesters them from the outside world.

574336.title: Eternal Code
574336.description: After a CEO and her husband refuse to support new technology that would sustain human life at a highly unethical cost, they are kidnapped.

574353.title: Abejas Asesinas (Doblado)
574353.description: Cuando un camión que transporta un enjambre de abejas se estrella, un pueblo es atacado. Ahora, un sheriff y un abejero deben salvar a los locales.

576722.title: Alien Strain
576722.description: An innocent man suspected of his girlfriend’s vanishing on a camping trip sees her return there alive a year later, but now she is an alien mutant.

577298.title: Omega Code
577298.description: An action-packed struggle for good and evil occurs when cyberwarfare attempts to manipulate the code of Biblical prophecies to start the end of days.

580232.title: Extinction: Patient Zero
580232.description: The clock is ticking, as scientists trapped in a safe room learn if they are infected by a deadly virus and can escape the activated safety protocols.

584637.title: The Key
584637.description: A British academic follows clues laid centuries before by Dante and Hieronymus Bosch to solve a series of murders inspired by the seven deadly sins.

587005.title: Peripheral
587005.description: A writer starts her second novel, but new software wraps her up in a mind control experiment, as she desperately tries to make her deadline.

587115.title: Otherlife
587115.description: Two inventors make a virtual reality drug with ground-breaking potential, but when this powerful narcotic lands in the wrong hands, the true dangers emerge.

590392.title: Memories
590392.description: The anime anthology classic from the creator of “Akira” featuring three visually incredible stories from the top animation studios in Japan.

590713.title: The Tangle
590713.description: In the future, where a web of nanobots connects all and eliminates any violence, a secret agency must solve an impossible crime: the perfect murder,

592399.title: Go / Don't Go
592399.description: The last human on earth feels his sanity slipping away when he becomes obsessed with the idea that someone is trying to make contact with him.

592423.title: Nina of the Woods
592423.description:
When an aspiring actress joins a supernatural reality show crew for a journey through 
the woods, things take an unexpected and dark turn.

599230.title: Incarnation
599230.description: A man wakes up on a bench without any idea who he is until he is shot dead by four masked assassins. The man wakes on the same bench thinking his death was a dream until the assassins return and despite his attempts to escape, they kill him again. Stuck in this hellish loop, he tries to unravel the mystery and with each death he gets closer to the truth.

600671.title: Against the Clock
600671.description: In this sci-fi thriller, a former CIA operative gets back into the field to find out what happened to her husband —but the CIA keeps getting in her way.

602434.title: S.N.U.B.
602434.description: With intel about an impending nuclear attack in London, a junior politician flees to an underground bunker that becomes a target for escaped convicts.

604440.title: Let's Dream
604440.description: Let, a reclusive, insomniac photographer, is hired to photograph a mysterious client in the forest late one night, and soon finds himself pulled into a bizarre, otherworldly quest.

605801.title: Alterverse
605801.description: A documentary filmmaker and her husband are recording camera footage throughout their house when they discover an alternate universe.

606642.title: Survival Games
606642.description: In the near future, a group of contestants play a televised game in Russia where those voted off must conquer their worst fears or die trying.

606891.title: The Arbors
606891.description: A lonely man's life begins to fracture and break after he finds a small creature that bonds with him and carries out his heart’s darkest wishes.

608851.title: Doors
608851.description: The appearance of a number of mysterious alien door portals around the world brings humanity to a crisis point in finding out just what they mean.

618271.title: Parallel
618271.description: Raw consequences arise when a group of friends find a mirror portal to a multiverse where what they learn there can never be escaped from.

620274.title: The Butterfly Effect 3: Revelations
620274.description: After disavowing time travel for its unintended consequences, Sam makes an exception in order to solve the mystery of his girlfriend’s murder.

622272.title: Lockdown: 2025
622272.description: When a highly contagious virus puts the entire country on lockdown, enforced by martial law, one family learns they’re not safe in their own home.

622424.title: Breakdown
622424.description: A man finds himself the lone mortal hope for the quarantined survivors of a virus that raged and killed most of the Earth’s population.

623289.title: Channeling
623289.description: In a not-too-distant future where people broadcast online every moment of their lives, a soldier on leave investigates his brother’s suspicious death.

629132.title: Infinitum: Subject Unknown
629132.description: A woman trapped in a mysterious world with seemingly endless options must find a way to alter her reality if she wants to escape the madness.

629541.title: Assassin 33 A.D. - Director's Cut: Black Easter
629541.description: After a billionaire funds a group of innovative thinkers who produce a time machine, they discover a terrorist plot to kill Jesus Christ.

629802.title: The Coming
629802.description: An end-of-days thriller about a group of young friends who must use The Book to get through a vivid and destructive implosion of life as we know it.

630370.title: Sender
630370.description: The discovery on a remote island of an amnesiac woman and her increasingly impressive psychic powers kicks off a bloody international race to find her.

631171.title: Paradise Lost
631171.description: A thriller about the deep Central America rain forest that a team of dedicated scientists must try to keep from being deforested with chemical sprays.

631173.title: Mind Storm
631173.description: “Sharknado” star Ian Ziering plays a married video game programmer who is unaware that his employer is embedding mind control messages in the apps.

631193.title: Curvature
631193.description: An  intriguing sci-fi drama about an engineer who risks everything to go back in time to stop herself from committing a murder she now regrets.

631473.title: ALAG - He Is Different - He Is Alone
631473.description: An orphan boy, considered strange from his years kept in a basement, is abducted by a rehab scientist for experiments once he displays psychic powers.

631544.title: Monsters of Man
631544.description: An illegal U.S. military op goes awry when killer robots are unleashed on heroin producers in Southeast Asia and end up wiping out an entire village.

636743.title: Night Drive
636743.description: The life of a tech bro-turned-rideshare driver is changed forever after picking up a chatty Aussie expat and taking her to her ex-boyfriend's house.

638163.title: Night of the Undead
638163.description: A happily married woman comes to learn her seemingly perfect husband may not only be an alien but a murderer she must kill before he gets her first.

639804.title: The Wave
639804.description: When an insurance lawyer goes out on the town with his friend to celebrate a promotion, he is dosed with a hallucinogen that changes his life forever.

640130.title: Entombed
640130.description: After a pandemic destroys the last of an already delicate civilization, a man ventures out to find shelter in a world filled with danger.

641426.title: Alternate Ground
641426.description: An extraterrestrial mystery unfolds after a 13-year-old boy is found unconscious on the street and begins exhibiting a rash of unexplained behaviors.

642398.title: Repeat
642398.description: When a psychologist makes a breakthrough discovery in communicating beyond this world, his daughter lands in the frightening crossfires.

646735.title: The Chain Reaction
646735.description: A chance meeting with a scientist turns a pair of tourists in the central Australian countryside into the targets of a nuclear facility’s assassins.

648137.title: Before I'm Dead
648137.description: In the wake of his wife’s death, a grieving young man slowly succumbs to agoraphobia until the laws of time and space begin to unravel around him.

649963.title: Freaks
649963.description: A little girl who has been shut away from the outside world by her father soon discovers a dangerous universe awaiting beyond her front door.

649967.title: The Endless
649967.description: Two brothers must re-examine their belief systems when they get a message to revisit the end-of-days UFO death cult they escaped from 10 years ago.

650262.title: Bonded in Blood
650262.description: Two parents grieving their young son’s murder become involved in the husband’s scientific push to clone their dead child – with terrible consequences.

650463.title: Await Further Instructions
650463.description: When a strange event traps a family inside their house, increasingly disturbing instructions on TV pull them into a vortex of paranoia and violence.

652101.title: Static (Español)
652101.description: Un experto en marketing, un estudiante de neurocirugía y un genio informático crean un chip de comunicación telepática que se implanta en el cerebro.

654679.title: Night Cries
654679.description: A man takes part in a series of troubling experiments with drug therapy in an apocalyptic setting as he tries to get back home before it's too late.

658933.title: Infrared Dreams
658933.description: In the future, a captive woman undergoes psychological and emotional testing by her abductor while learning that he may not be her biggest concern.

661451.title: Sensation
661451.description: Inducted into a secret superhuman DNA program, a postman learns that he'll be able to receive, control, and send information based on others' senses.

663213.title: Pursued (Broadcast Edit)
663213.description: When Ben Keats develops a revolutionary tracking system, he must protect his career and family from a ruthless, homicidal headhunter.

666126.title: Beverly H.
666126.description: Personal and global complications arise, when the CEO of a Beverly Hills biotech company and her top scientist create the first life extension drug.

668090.title: Incontrol
668090.description: College kids develop a machine that projects their consciousness onto others, allowing them to live inside their rich and beautiful fellow students.

672464.title: Godsend
672464.description: When their eight-year-old son dies, a grieving couple turns to an enigmatic geneticist who successfully clones their child—with terrifying results.

673686.title: Jet Stream
673686.description: A young scientist and a meteorologist team up to get to the bottom of what is causing these jet streams to level cities and bring down airplanes.

676658.title: Antiviral
676658.description: A pitchman at a clinic that harvests viruses from famous people to inject into their fans must unravel a celebrity mystery to save his own life.

677018.title: Only
677018.description: After a comet releases a mysterious plague threatening to kill all women on the planet, a couple is put to the ultimate test as they try to survive.

680718.title: Fireball
680718.description: Inspector Ava Williams investigates a prison fire and traces it to its source: an inmate seeking revenge against those who put him behind bars.

681195.title: Rocket Attack U.S.A.
681195.description: At the height of the Cold War, a CIA officer and a Russian double agent must stop the USSR from launching a surprise missile attack on the U.S.

682175.title: Stonados
682175.description: When an unprecedented weather event puts the Eastern Seaboard under siege, a former storm chaser’s untested theory is the only chance of stopping it.

682349.title: Arctic Void
682349.description: All but three men vanish from a tourist ship in the Arctic and fear becomes the master when a dark truth emerges that compels them to ally or perish.

684144.title: Devil's Gate
684144.description: While investigating a woman's disappearance, an FBI agent encounters an unholy force locked away in a booby-trapped, middle-of-nowhere farmhouse.

686221.title: Firequake
686221.description: An introduction to Helios, a revolutionary clean coal energy source so powerful it rivals the force of the sun and will solve the energy crisis.

686327.title: Harmony
686327.description: A wounded soldier begins to suspect the military medical facility where she’s been placed isn’t for her recovery, but for something sinister.

687555.title: The Call Up
687555.description: A group of online gamers invited to participate in a state-of-the-art virtual reality game find themselves trapped inside a real-life shoot ‘em up.

689243.title: Toxic Skies
689243.description: A brilliant doctor with the World Health Organization uncovers the real cause behind an epidemic: the U.S. government's secret chemtrail program.

689316.title: Ants On a Plane
689316.description: On their return home from a Caribbean eco-paradise, passengers board an ill-fated plane with a super-organism whose only imperative is survival.

692134.title: The Prototype
692134.description: An agent is subjected to alien experimentation and wakes up 300 years into the future. With Earth now destroyed, he is the only hope for mankind.

694472.title: The Girl
694472.description: A kidnapped woman is rescued by a young boy, and in return is compelled to save him from the horrors that lie in his very own home.

695214.title: Storm
695214.description: A meteorology professor sets out to derail his top-secret weather-manipulating invention after learning the military wants to use it as a weapon.

698078.title: Apollo 18
698078.description: Decades-old found footage involving three astronauts and an abandoned, secret NASA mission reveals why the U.S. has never returned to the moon.

702748.title: The Serpent's Stone
702748.description: On holiday in a seaside town known for UFO sightings, Joana becomes immersed in an abduction story after running over a man and befriending his widow.

703913.title: Meltdown: Days of Destruction
703913.description: A scientist tries to protect his family after an experiment meant to destroy an asteroid instead shifts Earth's orbit closer to the sun.

704490.title: The Last Survivors
704490.description: In the near future when society collapses and water becomes scarce, 17-year-old Kendal fights a violent water baron’s henchmen to keep a well open.

707525.title: Cerebrum
707525.description: A sizable sum of money convinces Tom to become his estranged father’s lab rat in a memory transfer study when he commits a crime he can’t remember.

707535.title: Destination Marfa
707535.description: A road trip becomes a nightmare when four lifelong friends take a fateful shortcut through the small, peculiar West Texas town of Marfa.

707541.title: High Voltage
707541.description: After lightning strikes the front woman of a fledgling band, she develops an edgy and electrifying touch that could launch them into stardom.

707583.title: Shimmer
707583.description: A forensics examiner in the deep South becomes baffled by a killer of possibly otherworldly origins that turns its victims into piles of gemstones.

707589.title: Synapse
707589.description: A memory dealer finds himself on the run from federal narcotics agents determined to keep the secrets in his mind hidden from the world forever.

707625.title: 11 A.M.
707625.description: Dr. Jung and his colleagues successfully travel into the future of the following day, only to discover the facility in ruins and everyone vanished.

708086.title: Meander
708086.description: After accepting a ride from a mysterious stranger, Lisa wakes up in a labyrinthian series of strange tubes full of deadly traps at every turn.

708343.title: Meteor: First Impact
708343.description: A scientist races against the clock in an attempt to save Earth from a series of deadly meteor attacks.

709943.title: Incident at Montauk
709943.description: Jed Logan comes to discover his UFO sighting may be linked to a secret government project which leads him down a dangerous path to uncover the truth.

711152.title: Dark Winter
711152.description: Fearing for the safety of their children, two parents embark on a dangerous mission against the great evil that is the council of Ashton Falls.

712338.title: Alien Rising
712338.description: A savvy ex-homeland security agent is forced to go to a remote island to help the military unlock the secrets of an extraterrestrial technology.

714665.title: Looker
714665.description: To clear his name in the deaths of three commercial actresses, a Beverly Hills plastic surgeon chases clues that lead him to a global conglomerate.

724571.title: Before the Fall
724571.description: A meteor is heading straight for Earth and the world's population is thrown into chaos as it decides how to spend the final 72 hours of life.

724867.title: The Colony
724867.description: Forced underground by the next ice age, a struggling outpost of survivors fights to preserve humanity against a threat even more savage than nature.

100001394.title: Carnifex
100001394.description: On their quest into the Australian Outback to track the animals left displaced by bushfires, a trio discovers a terrifying species and realize they're the ones being tracked.

0300005160.title: The Triangle
0300005160.description: After a large number of cargo ships disappear into the Bermuda Triangle, a specialist team uncovers a truth more disturbing than mythical legend.

0300009966.title: The Twilight Zone
0300009966.description: In this revival of the classic anthology series, host Forest Whitaker leads us on a mysterious journey into the deepest recesses of the human psyche.

0300005692.title: Day 5
0300005692.description: A group of survivors struggle to stay awake because sleep is now lethal. Battling fatigue and staying alert are essential to stay alive.

03615.title: CAT. 8
03615.description: The fate of all humankind is in the hands of a stubborn scientist whose warnings about an apocalyptic climate event have been too long ignored.

0300009482.title: Ring of Fire
0300009482.description: An oil rig triggers volcanic eruptions across the globe that could mean the end of humanity if a young activist can't stop the ripple effect.
